Register now for BRODEUR GOALIE CLINIC powered by @brodeurhockeyschool 

8 sessions will run June through July at the Middletown Sports Complex! Learn from professional and high level goaltenders! 1.5 hours of on-ice training and 1.5 of off-ice each day. Open to boys and girls, 12-18 years-old! Spots are limited to 28 goalies. To register and for more details visit the Link in bio.
